Bagel train and the team are #1. The best bagels in town. Always clean and fresh. Love all the bagel sandwiches and  selection Of coffee. Every Sunday it is our tradition that the girls and  I Pick up a dozen bagels for the week a pound of smoked Whitefish and go home for family breakfast and enjoy our Sunday Morning. I remember my mom shipping me bagels monthly to Arizona since I could not get a good bagel. Hint. The freeze well Double bagged and zipped locked. Let the defrost the nigh before. Oh.  The chicken salad is out of this world. Thanks bagel train.
